data.description: This Wylie East home is one that you won't want to miss out on!  Sitting at the end of the cul de sac with a huge backyard and covered patio makes a great place for large gatherings.  There's plenty of space inside to spread out as well with the huge living room that includes tons of built ins and wood look ceramic tile flooring, spacious kitchen with breakfast bar, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  There's also a walk in pantry to store plenty of things.  The dining room is really spacious and will hold a great sized dining table.  There are four bedrooms, one of which could be an office as well, and they offer the split floorplan.  This home has been very well maintained and is ready for the new owner to love it too!  Schedule your showing today so you don't miss out!
